%20association%20and%20collective%20bargaining,%20this%20is%20reported%20under%202-23-b-i%20in%20this%20Standard%20or%203-3-c%20in&amp;nbsp;GRI%203:%20Material%20Topics%202021.%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&amp;nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EGuidance%20to%202-30-a%3C/span%3E%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThe%20organization%20is%20required%20to%20report%20the%20percentage%20of%20its%20employees%20whose%20working%20conditions%20and%20terms%20of%20employment%20are%20regulated%20by%20one%20or%20more%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements.%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&amp;nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThe%20percentage%20of%20employees%20covered%20by%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements%20is%20calculated%20using%20the%20following%20formula:&amp;nbsp;%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3ENumber%20of%20employees%20covered%20by%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements%20/%20Total%20number%20of%20employees%20reported%20under%202-7-a%20x%20100%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&amp;nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThe%20employees%20covered%20by%20collective%20bargaining%20agreements%20are%20those%20employees%20to%20whom%20the%20organization%20is%20obligated%20to%20apply%20the%20agreement.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20none%20of%20the%20employees%20are%20covered%20by%20a%20collective%20bargaining%20agreement,%20the%20percentage%20reported%20is%20zero.%20An%20employee%20covered%20by%20more%20than%20one%20collective%20bargaining%20agreement%20only%20needs%20to%20be%20counted%20once.%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThis%20requirement%20does%20not%20ask%20for%20the%20percentage%20of%20employees%20represented%20by%20a%20works%20council%20or%20belonging%20to%20trade%20unions,%20which%20can%20be%20different.%20The%20percentage%20